name: Dark Matter Calabi Yau
short_description:
Based on some mathematical insight from string theory and Dimensional Analysis at the center of the tetrahedron should be the Calabi-Yau as well this helps us to visualize how photons (at c**-2) can turn a quanta of space into a particle as well as a deep insight into how Quantum entanglement works...  and how information can be sent through space quantum entanglement 

I'm still working on a space-time frame of tetrahedrons with there Calabi-Yau is in the center,.. I hope to check this model with the Quantum Mechanical model as well as with experimenters to see if we can get more precision then the known Quantum Mechanics, which means a better understanding of our reality, space-time and I hope Dark Matter, I think that the "Calabi-Yau's and Dark Matter" might be the same thing ...   and they are closely guarded dynamic engines of space and particles...
summary: cool simulation of dark matter hiding inside space and a electron
